        <h1 class="mb-3">How Do You Know When an Illustration is Done?</h1>
        <div class="podcast-title">Thoughts on Illustration</div>
        <div class="text-muted mb-4">December 10, 2024 at 8:00 AM</div>

        <audio controls class="audio-player" data-guid="8670c38b-b1ba-4faf-af12-0ed85917dc2a">
